data.description: Rare 6 bedroom home with Loft located in one of West Sac's most desirable area's.. Bridgeway Lakes Community. This spacious home features lots of cabinet space and granite counter tops in the kitchen. Remodeled master shower/with bench. All good sized rooms with big closets. Home also features a nice Lemon tree in the back & extended driveway. You will enjoy this great neighborhood. It features lots of Parks and a wonderful Lake to take a stroll around + walking trails. Great home to raise a family in.
